        "paragraph_index": 0,
        "text": "## Result\n\n**No stability constants measured in supercritical CO₂ are available in the NIST SRD-46 database.**\n\nThe database's `solvent_name` field contains only **H₂O (water)** — all 79,063 stability-constant records in SRD-46 were measured in aqueous solution. There are no entries for supercritical CO₂, organic solvents, or any other non-aqueous medium.",
